snippet.title: Heroes of the Citadel Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Become a  Funtico Pioneer https://pioneers.funtico.com/?btag=100006

Step into Heroes of the Citadel to unite a world torn apart. A mysterious force has seeded chaos in the once-serene Entagon. A group of unsuspecting heroes emerges, ready to combat the darkness. The fate of the world lies in your hands. Assemble your team and become one of the Heroes of the Citadel.

Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2774710/Heroes_of_the_Citadel/?curator_clanid=26335619
